#!/usr/bin/perl

=head1 NAME

bgpmon_cpm_db_reset
A script to reset a BGP database to an empty state

=cut

=head1 DEPENDENCIES

The following Perl modules must be installed to use this script:

Getopt::Long
Cwd

=cut

=head1 USAGE

> ./bgpmon_cpm_db_reset --dbname=database --dblogin=username

=cut

